<promed@promedmail.org>
[Citrus growers are relieved, to say the least, but the removal and burning
of infected trees is a massive undertaking. One wonders how long it will
take for Evergreen Farms, owned by Pacific Century Production, to resume
planting and production. - Mod.DH]
